(BETA) Information Tool about installed Applications.

## Major Features:
1. List all installed apps (01f).
2. Sort apps by Name, Package, Install date, Permissions, in Ascending or Descending Order (03l28).
3. Number of Dangerous Permissions are in bold (03n30).
4. Filter by application state: Launchable, System (03k27).
5. SHORT CLICK to access Application info: storage, cache, controls... (01k10).
6. LONG PRESS to launch Application (02a12).
7. Device Information: Memory; Screen Width, Height, Density; ... (03b18).

## Minor Features:
- English and Italian localization.
- No Permission Required.
- Requires Android 1.6 and above.

## What's New:
(03n30) Number of Dangerous Permissions are in bold & Optimized images.

## Keywords:
apk, app, apps, details, info, information, installed, packages, system, tool, utility.

